headline: AppLovin to Announce Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2025 Results
summary: PALO ALTO, Calif., January 07, 2026--AppLovin Corporation, (NASDAQ: APP) ("AppLovin" or the "Company") the leading marketing platform, today announced it will report financial results for the fourth quarter and fiscal year 2025 on Wednesday, February 11, 2026 after the U.S. stock market closes.
